牡犡的薑餅麵包症（由Clionna引起）: maladie du pain d'epice [=gingerbread disease of oyster]

仔鼠致死性腸病毒: lethal intestinal virus of infant mice (LIVIM)

捷克森紐西蘭兔: III/J strain New Zealand white rabbit

小腸自發性絨毛萎縮: idiopathic villous atrophy of the small intestine

紅血球膜性溶血: hemolytic disorders of red cell membrane

紅血球酵素性溶血: hemolytic disorders of red cell enzymes

與「血」有關之字首: hemo-; haemo-; hem-; haem-; hema-; hemato-

紅血球計數: erythrocyte or red blood cell count

人腸道孤兒病毒: ECHO virus (enteric cytopathogenic human orphan virus)

畢特納乳癌病毒（畢特納發現對於A品系小鼠帶有乳癌高發生率之病毒）: Bittner mammary tumor virus [=Bittner's milk factor]

倉鼠之末端迴腸炎: terminal ileitis of hamsters [=regional ileitis; wet tai]

第 I 型糖尿病（胰島素依賴型糖尿病）: type I diabetes (Insulin-depedent diabetes mellitus; IDDM)
